-SERGENT NELSON
TO THE INMATE PROCESSING CENTER

14:10.850 --> 14:13.548
SERGENT NELSON TO THE
INMATE PROCESSING CENTER.

14:22.078 --> 14:23.079
-NO TOUCHING.

14:23.210 --> 14:24.646
-BRADY, DON'T.

14:24.776 --> 14:26.735
PLEASE, THEY'LL PUT
YOU BACK IN SOLITARY.

14:26.866 --> 14:28.171
-FIVE MINUTES.

14:32.262 --> 14:34.003
-I COULDN'T WAIT ANOTHER
SIX MONTHS NOT SEEING YOU.

14:34.917 --> 14:36.353
-DID YOU GET THE BOAT?

14:36.484 --> 14:38.529
-IT'S THE KIND OF BOAT
WE ALWAYS DREAMED ABOUT.

14:39.226 --> 14:41.228
IT'S SO FAST, IT'S LIKE
YOU'RE FLYING OVER THE WATER.

14:43.143 --> 14:44.927
LAST NIGHT I DREAMT I WAS IN IT.

14:46.407 --> 14:47.843
YOU WERE SWIMMING TOWARD ME,

14:48.757 --> 14:51.107
AND THE SUN WAS
RISING BEHIND YOU.

14:51.238 --> 14:55.198
YOU WERE FREE, BRADY.
WE WERE RACING OFF TOGETHER.

14:56.417 --> 14:58.462
-YOU DREAM THAT
SAME DREAM TONIGHT.

14:59.942 --> 15:01.248
-I WILL.

15:02.423 --> 15:03.728
-SO WILL I.

15:12.041 --> 15:13.390
-HERE YOU GO.

15:17.133 --> 15:18.700
OKAY, ENJOY.

15:23.618 --> 15:24.488
-HI HONEY.

15:24.619 --> 15:25.794
-HI MOM.

15:25.925 --> 15:27.709
-CAN I GET YOU
SOMETHING TO EAT?

15:27.839 --> 15:31.060
-UM NO, I'LL JUST HAVE
A GLASS OF WATER, THANKS.

15:31.191 --> 15:33.497
-OH, COME ON, NOW. YOU GOTTA
HAVE SOMETHING TO EAT.

15:33.628 --> 15:35.543
LET ME MAKE YOU A SANDWICH.

15:35.673 --> 15:37.110
HOW ABOUT TODAY'S SPECIAL HUH?

15:37.240 --> 15:38.502
A TUNA MELT.

15:39.155 --> 15:41.418
-MOM, I DON'T WANT
ANYTHING TO EAT, OKAY?

15:41.549 --> 15:42.506
JUST WATER.

15:43.290 --> 15:47.033
-OKAY, OKAY. ONE GLASS
OF WATER COMING UP.

15:47.163 --> 15:48.164
-THANK YOU.

15:48.295 --> 15:50.297
-ALL RIGHT, COME HERE, DAUGHTER.

15:50.427 --> 15:52.952
SIT DOWN. I WANT
TO TALK WITH YOU.

15:54.954 --> 15:59.393
SO FILL ME IN, HUH? HOW GOES
THE SAGA OF MATTHEW AND SLADE?

15:59.523 --> 16:00.829
WHAT ARE THE LATEST HIGHLIGHTS?

16:00.960 --> 16:03.223
-NONE, AND THERE'S
NOT GONNA BE ANY

16:03.353 --> 16:06.617
TOMORROW OR THE NEXT DAY.
SO JUST STOP ASKING ALL RIGHT?

16:07.575 --> 16:09.707
-HONEY, YOU'RE BEING SILLY.

16:10.665 --> 16:11.971
AVOIDING BOTH OF
THEM ISN'T GOING

16:12.101 --> 16:13.798
TO MAKE YOU FEEL ANY BETTER.

16:14.886 --> 16:16.236
SWEETIE, YOU'RE GONNA
HAVE TO RESOLVE THIS,

16:16.366 --> 16:17.585
ONE WAY OR ANOTHER.

16:17.715 --> 16:19.108
-HOW?

16:19.239 --> 16:20.675
AND IF I CHOOSE ONE,
THEN I'M GONNA JUST

16:20.805 --> 16:22.807
RUIN ALL OF OUR FRIENDSHIPS.

16:23.504 --> 16:26.463
-ALL RIGHT THEN, DON'T CHOOSE.

16:27.334 --> 16:29.771
SPEND TIME WITH BOTH OF
THEM, BE FRIENDS, YOU KNOW?

16:29.901 --> 16:32.339
DO THINGS TOGETHER, HAVE FUN,

16:32.469 --> 16:34.689
AND JUST LET NATURAL
SELECTION TAKE OVER.

16:34.819 --> 16:36.604
-NATURAL SELECTION.

16:36.734 --> 16:37.953
-YEAH.

16:38.562 --> 16:40.956
SWEETIE THE MORE TIME THE
THREE OF YOU SPEND TOGETHER,

16:41.087 --> 16:43.698
IT'S GOING TO BECOME
APPARENT TO ALL OF YOU

16:43.828 --> 16:46.483
WHICH TWO WERE MEANT
TO BE TOGETHER.

16:46.614 --> 16:50.096
-YEAH, WHICH IS PROBABLY GONNA
END UP BEING MATT AND SLADE.

16:50.226 --> 16:52.228
THEN THEY'RE BOTH
JUST GONNA DUMP ME.

16:53.099 --> 16:54.491
-WELL MAYBE...

16:56.102 --> 16:59.235
BUT, SWEETIE, AT LEAST IT
WILL BE RESOLVED, OKAY?

16:59.366 --> 17:00.715
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

17:35.489 --> 17:37.839
-SUMMER, CAN WE
TALK ABOUT SOMETHING?

17:37.969 --> 17:39.362
-NOT NOW MATT.

18:20.534 --> 18:23.189
-LIEUTENANT ALTERMAN, COME TO
THE PROPERTY ROOM.

18:23.319 --> 18:25.800
LIEUTENANT ALTERMAN, PLEASE
COME TO THE PROPERTY ROOM.

18:36.202 --> 18:38.160
SERGENT MASON, YOU'RE
NEEDED AT THE FRONT WINDOW.

18:38.291 --> 18:40.336
SERGENT MASON TO THE
FRONT WINDOW, PLEASE.

19:01.662 --> 19:03.490
-MAN: FREEZE!

